column4: NSLOCTEXT("[FC3CF65A4C86C6BE142F24BB0791D482]", "ECC0CD5E48253FB08B7D219E6020ECF5", "I lost, but you guys are nothing!")
NSLOCTEXT("[FC3CF65A4C86C6BE142F24BB0791D482]", "A7ABD6C2496FDD2EDA07C4BA91AFE35E", "Don\'t be a sore loser. You even sneak attacked us by surprise.")
NSLOCTEXT("[FC3CF65A4C86C6BE142F24BB0791D482]", "454AC6B8476C6EFC65FB3EB91E788578", "Ugh! You leave me no choice but to...")
NSLOCTEXT("[FC3CF65A4C86C6BE142F24BB0791D482]", "830ABE9A474F58A9E1EE799B282C2DD5", "In that city of yours, I\'ll show you how strong I am! Just you watch!")
